,Recommended,240760,12542930,"Posted: 18 October, 2014",all,CPT Rhodes,"Recruit bums with high luck and shotgun skills. Use a Native American girl to recruit a stat boosting goat into your party and get angry as some raider kills it. Get down-dressed by your superior officer for wearing a dog collar. Botch a safe cracking and have your buddy fix it for you so you can give it another try real quick. Botch it again and kill the both of you. Build your own set of unique characters. Allow them to wander the wastes and influence it with more freedom than most games provide. Mod guns. Smoke cigarettes. Harass youths.A role playing treasure trove with the atmosphere of Fallout, the combat of X-Com, NPC collection of Suikoden, unforgiving and brazen RPG elements. Ignore the biased mainstream reviews. Ignore the nit pickers. Revel in this post apocalyptic gem.The only major thing this game needs is a DLC where you get to (virtually) shake the hand of Brian Fargo.Worth my money; and yours."
