76561198017681447,Recommended,240760,23872916,"Posted: 27 June, 2016",all,ferretsrule,"An adult version of another nameless post-apocalyptic RPG, based on a sound concept with a good backstory. If you want a good RPG with choices that matter, characters that are very detailed (not to make but to actually play), gameplay that is complex and challenging, and plenty to explore that has some relevance to the actual story, then is the game for you. The only con to the game is that if you’re not used to hard-core old school RPG's then this will be a challenge to you. It will not forgive, it will not let you get away with your mistakes, it is not for the faint hearted. If you've only played those other for well-known RPGs that hold your hand and tell you what you can and can't do then this will be a shock to your system. But if you go at it with an open mind and don't mind putting some time into the background and enjoy and good story you will be rewarded, thumbs up!"
