y could have easily turned this into a DLC ridden abomination and they didn't, (don't get me wrong guys, if you want to throw out a colorado DLC I would gladly open my pockets for you again, no, any DLC, red boots perhaps?)Thank you again inXile, your mastery of the genre is duly noted, I am extreamly satisfied with the experiance and I am hoping for more sooner then 2038!"
